Ughelli- A group, Concerned Itsekiri Youths for Development, (CIYD), has called on Itsekiri nation and the Delta state government to appreciate Comrade Monday Agbeyi, Chairman of Abigborodo Community, in Warri North Local Government Area of the state for his leadership role in the growth and development of Itsekiri nation. In a statement signed by its President, Mr. Tuoyo Amaju, and Public Relations Officer, Ms. Rose Omatie, the Itsekiri professional group, said Agbeyi needed to be appreciated for his rare gift in mobilisation and organisation with a determined conviction to develop the Abigborodo Community in particular and Delta State as a whole. According to the group, ”Our commendation of Comrade Monday Agbeyi which is coming on the heels of his birthday on Christmas Day, is underscored by his passionate ability to effectively organise and mobilise the Itsekiri people for grassroots development.” EXPOSED - HOW LAGOS DOCTOR DISCOVERED MAJOR REASONS WHY MOST WIVES NOW HEAVILY CHEATS ON THEIR HUSBANDS AND THE PERMANENT SECRET TO SEXUALLY SATISFYING THEIR WIVES. DON'T BE A VICTIM! ”We join other Itsekiri at home and in the diaspora to wish him a blissful birthday, long life, prosperity, robust health, sound mind and unspeakable joy as he continue to play his role as an uncommon leader of repute.” ”Undoubedly, Comrade Agbeyi’s existence on earth is one primed to serve God and humanity. For this, we pray the Almighty to continue to empower him to achieve more for our appreciative people,” the statement added. SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION